title: Rat Queens (2017-) #6
description: “THE COLOSSAL MAGIC NOTHING,” Part One Having escaped the nefarious clutches of the insidious trickster Castiwyr, the Rat Queens return to Palisade with piles of gold and are in a mood to party. But Palisade has a new resident: a strange wizard that wishes to end the suffering of others. Forever.
author: Kurtis J. Wiebe
